## this is package idea


## story

  - when playing youtube pop songs, display a text area with lyrics, called transcript
  - lyrics is auto-scrolling along with the playing
  - when video pause, pause scrolling
  - highlight the line of lyrics according the timestamp


## tech stack

  - a react component 
  - using vtt subscript as prop?
  - current timestamp is state


